{"tid":1908091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【區議會動議】大河道一號休憩處正式命名「十一人民抗暴紀念花園」","createTime":"2020-03-03T04:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T07:23:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8d2396c0d0b5f67ff0debaf26eeaff18d9e819","tid":1908091,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"【區議會動議】大河道一號休憩處正式命名「十一人民抗暴紀念花園」<br />\n<br />\n過去多年，荃灣大河道多個休憩處未有命名，僅以一號、二號、三號休憩處以作識別。<br />\n<br />\n2019年10月1日，荃灣中五學生參與反修例抗爭活動期間，不幸在荃灣大河道一號休憩處遭到一名警長開槍實彈擊中胸部，傷重昏迷不醒，是香港1997年主權移交後首名被實彈槍傷的示威者。<br />\n<br />\n為紀念人民反抗暴政而在荃灣區內發生的悲劇事件，趙恩來議員將於2020年3月31日動議荃灣區議會把大河道一號休憩處正式命名「十一人民抗暴紀念花園」，告誡當權者停止血腥暴力鎮壓人民，不再重蹈覆轍。<br />\n<br />\n#荃灣區議會 #動議 #十一人民抗暴紀念花園<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107233492804621/posts/1272774269583865/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107233492804621%2Fposts%2F1272774269583865%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVprY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=b41b49f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107233492804621/posts/1272774269583865/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"a045364e14bb2f1396a6cd58b3aaadd8173a3690","tid":1908091,"uid":203783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"有冇人介紹下會經咩步驟去通過改名提議<br />\n一但開咗先例將來就有機會十八區嘅地標都改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6158abdd59d19f8bc83851c750a6b92ec60fff08","tid":1908091,"uid":34722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"區議會投票有法定效力咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c3659e8c4a874636ab014ff21b5803177ac1bb","tid":1908091,"uid":75648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc1c5038eafe47fb5083fcd4bbbb998c5b9ea00","tid":1908091,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT